nsidered when methotrexate is used with other potentially hepatotoxic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/94501/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Thalidomide, Belimumab, More', 'Cabozantinib, Avapritinib, Ripretinib, Copanlisib, Trametinib, Erdafitinib, Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Vandetanib, Palbociclib, Infigratinib, More', 1767369485);
